The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | Grant gets Divine thanks
                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Grant gets Divine thanks
                                Lucrative scandal                           
	London, Aug. 30 (PTI): A former prostitute who hit the headlines for her infamous 1995 encounter with Hugh Grant has publicly thanked the actor for changing her life after the scandal.        
	After the British star was arrested in Los Angeles with Hollywood prostitute Divine Brown, she went on to land a series of lucrative publicity deals to talk about her experience with the actor, reports the Daily Mail. Brown, real name Stella Thompson, quit prostitution after the furore and now lives in Atlanta.        
	 Thompson, 41, admits she will always be grateful to Grant for giving her a second chance at life.                                                                                                                                                          
